# What are number systems?

A number system is simply a system representing numbers!

Here's a chart breaking down the systems in this tutorial!

| System        | Base          | Range       |
| ------------- |:-------------:|------------:|
| decimal       | 10            | 0-9         |
| binary        | 2             | 0,1         |
| octal         | 8             | 0-7         |
| hexadecimal   | 16            | 0-9, A-F    |
